FIG. 2 is a front elevation view of the conformal hearing tip and the retention and extraction device of FIG. 1;


FIG. 3 is a perspective view of the retention and extraction device of FIG. 1;


FIG. 4 is an exploded perspective view showing the assembly of a conformal hearing aid tip, a completely in-the-canal hearing device and a retention and extraction device, constructed in accordance with a preferred embodiment of the present invention; and


FIG. 5 is a cross sectional view of an assembled conformal hearing aid tip, a completely in-the-canal hearing device, and a retention and extraction device constructed in accordance with a preferred embodiment of the present invention.
